name: In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Robert S. SEGUIN.

court.name: Supreme Court of the United States

parties: In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Robert S. SEGUIN.

opinions.text: Robert S. Seguin, of Milltown, New Jersey, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.

casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Robert S. SEGUIN.
No. D-2831.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 29, 2015.
